Business Brief -- Allied Products Corp.:
   Unit of Transamerica Sells
   Part of Its Stake in Firm
The filing indicated Transamerica Commercial received
91,344 shares Thursday to satisfy, in stock rather than cash,
certain dividend and redemption obligations Allied has to
Transamerica Commercial as a holder of Allied preferred
shares.
   Transamerica Commercial holds 569,655 of the Chicago-based
agricultural equipment and industrial products concern's
shares, all of which were received to satisfy dividend and
redemption obligations by Allied, the filing said.